snippet.title: Sega Master System - FA Tetris © 1990 FA Soft - Gameplay
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
FA Tetris is a Puzzle game, developed by Fresh Fishes and published by FA Soft, which was released in Korea in 1990.
